  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct used in posterior lumbar fixation. The model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes solvers) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two independent laboratories under ASTM F1717 loading. All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors have been assessed; one factor (Test conditions) falls below the required level due to a single test condition being evaluated. The intended use is limited to static compression-bending loading of non-cannulated pedicle screw constructs in adults with intact posterior elements, as described in the bound requirement and claim documents.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/req/f1717-compression-bending-noncannulated",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/claim/fea-f1717-static-compression-bending",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/model/fea-pedicle-screw-ensemble-v2",
  "bindsDataset": [
    "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/data/f1717-experimental-n11-lab1",
    "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/data/f1717-experimental-n11-lab2"
  ],
